      <div class="main-content">
        <h3>We Couldn't Process Your Payment</h3>
        <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
        <p>
          We're reaching out regarding your recent attempt to enroll in the
          <b>{{ propFirmName }}</b> prop firm challenge
          <b>(account size: {{ accountSize }}, total cost: {{ totalCost }})</b>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Unfortunately, your payment for this challenge was not successful.
        </p>
        <p>
          We understand that unexpected delays can occur. We're here to help you
          get started on your funded account journey as soon as possible.
        </p>

        <p>
          <b
            >Once you retry and your payment is successful, you'll receive
            immediate access to your dashboard and valuable resources to
            dominate your challenge.</b
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          We look forward to welcoming you to the BullBear Mastery community!
        </p>
        <p class="bbm-team sign">The BBM Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p
          style="
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-family: 'Squada One', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #007bff !important;
            letter-spacing: 0.3pt;
            font-size: 18px;
          "
        >
          Join Our Communities
        </p>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <a href="#" target="_blank"
            ><img
              src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/bullbearmastery.appspot.com/o/Assets%2Ficons%2Fdiscord.png?alt=media&token=27855001-07eb-4b3f-88ac-cdd4b25e154e"
              alt="Discord"
          /></a>
          <a href="#" target="_blank"
            ><img
              src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/bullbearmastery.appspot.com/o/Assets%2Ficons%2Finstagram.png?alt=media&token=fa7b882f-3701-4180-a4f0-eed7edd6cab8"
              alt="Instagram"
          /></a>
          <a href="#" target="_blank"
            ><img
              src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/bullbearmastery.appspot.com/o/Assets%2Ficons%2Fx.png?alt=media&token=90d72047-1f04-4868-b64a-fe4abd7b621f"
              alt="X"
          /></a>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px !important">
          Thank you for choosing BullBear Mastery.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px !important">
          Need help?
          <a href="https://bullbearmastery.com/contact-us" target="_blank"
            >Contact our customer support</a
          >
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 14px !important">
          &copy; 2024 BullBear Mastery. All Rights Reserved
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
